snippet.title: Ghost Master Complete Edition - Halloween Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Ghost Master Complete Edition's Discord Server: https://discord.gg/6QPFuf2dyM

"Ghost Master, The Bureau of Astral Affairs is delighted with your accomplishments. As a reward, you have been given three new Haunters that are sure to assist you during your terrifying visits to the mortal world…"

This is the first 3 custom ghosts are in, Torchy and Moribund are back after 18 years of waiting. Enjoy !
